{"tid":415240,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"128蚊餐蛋飯","createTime":"2017-09-26T23:24:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-27T15:10:37.000Z","uid":17835,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"e94f864517707bdf02e5ea99aa3fe58a3cfaf5c1","tid":415240,"uid":17835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:24:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072045_4ea75dd702f188c26f102d3e374baba6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072045_4ea75dd702f188c26f102d3e374baba6.jpg&h=a26e4381&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n少年食神：一分錢一分貨<br />\n東來居老闆、「少年食神」林澄光（Michael）說餐蛋飯貴得有道理，「好簡單一句，一分錢一分貨，我哋啲用料同幾十蚊一碟係唔同。」Michael如數家珍地說出餐肉、蛋和米也各有名堂，「最貴係豉油，我哋自己秘製，你出面食唔到」。他又澄清餐牌上根本沒有餐蛋飯，一般顧客難嚐，「只係有朋友想食得牙擦啲，我哋至整畀佢哋食，後來雜誌想介紹，先至登咗出嚟」。對於天價餐蛋飯引來網民批評，Michael感無奈，「啲人夾硬拉埋80後、90後嚟講，我係好欣賞好多90後都係勤力工作」。<br />\n經常光顧酒店高級食府的家庭醫生關嘉美稱，酒店百多元一客餐蛋飯不出奇，高級食肆會接受熟客「tailor made」（度身訂造）菜式。「你去半島嘉麟樓點餐蛋飯，起碼要200幾蚊」。她又說搵食艱難，「如果唔想浪費血汗錢，餐蛋飯自己番屋企煮啦」。<br />\n<br />\n$128餐蛋飯有乜料？<br />\n午餐肉：<br />\n金華火腿製成，非一般超市有售<br />\n<br />\n雞　蛋：<br />\n湖南衡陽雞蛋<br />\n<br />\n飯：<br />\n日本秋田小町米<br />\n<br />\n豉　油：<br />\n生抽、老抽、葱頭、海味和金華火腿調和秘製<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130615/18298314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130615%2F18298314&d=ET79mwu14G5d3JvAXnBCiMVakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=6b9b0e27\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Fart%2F20130615%2F18298314&h=92230a27\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/news/art/20130615/18298314</a><br />\n<br />\n大家仲記唔記得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n岩岩諗住open rice 間野<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072357_76ec5f514de65c85a6930f2e4ae7cb77.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072357_76ec5f514de65c85a6930f2e4ae7cb77.jpg&h=9396100f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/27/072403_75c8c723a9cb886e314010606731835d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F27%2F072403_75c8c723a9cb886e314010606731835d.jpg&h=c833fd22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係咪收左皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed8f6aef67d8f1f00941f2a8d136036577b1ac4c","tid":415240,"uid":76100,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:39:41.000Z","msg":"用支那蛋講到咁高級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27702cd29b38677191eb34ae82e25905e851a4c","tid":415240,"uid":63,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T23:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>用支那蛋講到咁高級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38c30e335f1117af29efdc3bfafbf1a7dab2684a","tid":415240,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T00:27:45.000Z","msg":"咁似食神個車仔麵"},{"pid":"febdeb654df2fb1aff40f6c11e97daa0a3f07b99","tid":415240,"uid":42734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-27T01:16:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>用支那蛋講到咁高級<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\